.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: british, thai, russian, argentine, turkish, indonesian, brazilian
7 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, guinea-pig, lizard, frog, dog, horse
 1. the turkish is on the left of the british##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 3. the owner of the frog is the brazilian##1
 4. the russian is on the left of the indonesian##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the argentine is the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the british is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the horse and the argentine##2
 9. the british is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
10. the thai is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | turkish | british | thai   | argentine | russian | indonesian |
| Pet           | frog | dog     | snake     | guinea-pig | lizard   | ferret   | horse    |

