.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, cola, coffee
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, british, argentine, american, german, egyptian, colombian
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the argentine##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the german##1
 3. the egyptian is on the right of the american##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the german##1
 5. the indian is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the american is between the person drinking milk and the egyptian##2
 7. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 8. the american is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the british##1
10. the indian is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | milk    | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate  | 7up  | coffee      | cola       | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | german | american | egyptian | colombian | indian | argentine | british  |

