.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: pop, blues, d&b, r&b, country, techno, indie
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, scooter, car, roller, airplane, taxi, quad-bike
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the fan of blues##1
3. the person driving the boat is between the fan of indie and the fan of pop##2
4. the fan of techno is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of pop##1
7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person driving the scooter is the fan of r&b##1
9. the fan of country is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | country | pop | d&b | indie      | blues      | techno |
| Transport     | scooter | taxi | quad-bike       | boat | car | airplane | roller |

