.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  photographer, dancer, lawyer, nurse, electrician, musician, analyst
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, skateboarding, skiing, rugby, swimming, tennis, baseball
1. the lawyer is on the left of the analyst##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the electrician##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the musician is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is swimming and the photographer##2
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
8. the musician is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | electrician | photographer | nurse | musician | dancer | lawyer     | analyst |
| Sport   | skiing   | rugby    | baseball    | swimming      | skateboarding  | sailing | tennis |

