 4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person drinking juice##2
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | mirinda    | sprite | soy-milk   | tea | water    | juice |
| Sport      | skiing | badminton | baseball    | climbing | swimming    | snowboarding | soccer  |

