.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, sprite, iced-tea, 7up, coffee, almond-milk
The people have 7 different jobs:  doctor, lawyer, social-worker, security-guard, manager, teacher, dancer
 1. the manager is on the left of the security-guard##1
 2. the doctor is on the left of the social-worker##1
 3. the teacher is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the manager is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 7. the lawyer is on the right of the teacher##1
 8. the doctor is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking tea##2
11. the manager is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | sprite  | 7up   | tea         | soy-milk     | almond-milk              | coffee    | iced-tea     |
| Job        | teacher | lawyer | manager | security-guard | dancer | doctor | social-worker |

