.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, western, martial-arts, comedy, sports, mystery, superhero
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, scooter, ship, bike, airplane, car, helicopter
1. the person watching spy movies is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching sports movies is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the airplane##2
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
9. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | comedy     | mystery | sports | martial-arts | superhero  | spy |
| Transport     | ship | bike | airplane   | van     | helicopter    | scooter | car   |

