.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, almond-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, juice
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, traveling, video-games, sudoku, dancing, camping, baking
1. the person who's hobby is camping is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is camping##2
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | lemonade       | juice         | hot-chocolate         | sprite   | almond-milk        | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | baking | video-games | reading | dancing | traveling | camping | sudoku  |

