.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, writing, chess, traveling, photography, filmmaking, fishing
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, golf, badminton, handball, climbing, basketball, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | fishing | filmmaking       | chess    | photography | traveling | writing     | skydiving       |
| Sport   | golf    | handball | basketball | climbing        | badminton | cycling | baseball |

