 3. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching family movies and the fan of funk##2
 4. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
 5. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is the fan of d&b##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
