.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-15::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, cola, 7up, juice, almond-milk, tea
There 7 different types of food: grapefruit, cucumber, cranberry, peach, orange, pepper, avocado
 1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
