 4. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking tea and the person eating grapefruit##2
 5. the person eating peach is the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person eating avocado is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person eating cranberry is the person eating cranberry##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
10. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk       | almond-milk | juice      | sprite | tea       | cola | 7up |
| Food       | pepper | cranberry    | orange | avocado    | cucumber | peach   | grapefruit |

