6. the dancer is on the left of the person eating apple##1
7. the coach is on the right of the musician##1
8. the designer is between the person eating kale and the dancer##2
9. the person eating kale is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
